{{Top|leg}}
'''Imaharatronics''' was a company that produced [[logic display sensor]]s for use in various models of [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. The [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droid]] [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] had a sensor constructed by this company.

==Behind the scenes==
This company is a reference to [[Grant Imahara]], a controller for R2-D2 in the [[prequel trilogy]].<ref name="Building Dictionary">{{SWArchive|url=eu/lit/ref/f20061031/index.html|text=Building a ''Complete Visual Dictionary''}}</ref>

